Acked-by: Lee Jones <lee.jones@linaro.org>
Tested-by: Lee Jones <lee.jones@linaro.org>
Link: http://patchwork.freedesktop.org/patch/msgid/1490280292-30466-1-git-send-email-vincent.abriou@st.com

